ck font-size="10pt"><fo:marker marker-class-name="current-topic-number">1</fo:marker><fo:block border-bottom="3pt solid black" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="18pt" font-weight="bold" id="install-ceph" keep-with-next.within-column="always" padding-top="16.8pt" space-after="16.8pt" space-before="0pt"><fo:block border-left-width="0pt" border-right-width="0pt" keep-with-next.within-column="always" line-height="100%"><fo:marker marker-class-name="current-header"> Ceph Configuration </fo:marker><fo:inline id="topic_jrc_5lz_ft"/><fo:inline id="_OPENTOPIC_TOC_PROCESSING_d75e1"/> Ceph Configuration </fo:block></fo:block><fo:block font-size="10pt" start-indent="25pt">
    <fo:block space-after="0.6em" space-before="0.6em" text-indent="0em">This page describes configuration, installation, and the integration of Ceph Block Storage
      with HP Helion<fo:inline border-left-width="0pt" border-right-width="0pt">OpenStack<fo:inline baseline-shift="20%" font-size="75%"><opentopic-i18n:text-fragment char-set="SymbolsSuperscript">®</opentopic-i18n:text-fragment></fo:inline></fo:inline>2.0. After the installation of Ceph you can
