    <fo:block font-size="10pt" line-height="12pt" space-before="0.6em">
      <fo:block font-family="sans-serif" font-weight="bold" id="preq" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before="15pt">Prerequisite</fo:block>
      <fo:block space-after="0.6em" space-before="0.6em" text-indent="0em">The deployer node must be setup before deploying Ceph. For more details on the installation
        of deployer node, refer to <fo:inline/><fo:basic-link color="blue" font-style="italic" internal-destination="DeployerInstall"> installation
        guide</fo:basic-link>.</fo:block>
    </fo:block>
    <fo:block font-size="10pt" line-height="12pt" space-before="0.6em">
      <fo:block font-family="sans-serif" font-weight="bold" id="install-procedure" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before="15pt">Installation Procedure</fo:block>
      <fo:block space-after="0.6em" space-before="0.6em" text-indent="0em">Perform the following procedures to configure, install, and the integrate the Ceph Block
        Storage with HP Helion OpenStack 2.0.</fo:block>
    </fo:block>
    <fo:block font-size="10pt" line-height="12pt" space-before="0.6em">
      <fo:block space-after="0.6em" space-before="0.6em" text-indent="0em">
        <fo:list-block id="ol_evc_k11_gt" provisional-distance-between-starts="5mm" provisional-label-separation="1mm" space-after="0.6em" space-before="0.6em">
          <fo:list-item space-after="1.5pt" space-before="1.5pt"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()" keep-together.within-line="always" keep-with-next.within-line="always"><fo:block font-weight="bold" text-align="start"><fo:inline/>1. </fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block>Login to the Deployer node.</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item>
          <fo:list-item space-after="1.5pt" space-before="1.5pt"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()" keep-together.within-line="always" keep-with-next.within-line="always"><fo:block font-weight="bold" text-align="start"><fo:inline/>2. </fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block>Create the Ceph configuration files (<fo:inline font-weight="bold">manually</fo:inline>) at
              <fo:inline font-family="monospace" font-size="10pt">~/helion-input/my_cloud/definition</fo:inline>. The example configuration files
            are available at <fo:inline/><fo:basic-link color="blue" font-style="italic" internal-destination="topic_trz_pgw_gt">Ceph
              Configuration
            files</fo:basic-link>.</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item>
          <fo:list-item space-after="1.5pt" space-before="1.5pt"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()" keep-together.within-line="always" keep-with-next.within-line="always"><fo:block font-weight="bold" text-align="start"><fo:inline/>3. </fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block>Copy the configuration files in the respective folder as shown in the screeshot
              below.<fo:block space-after="0.6em" space-before="0.6em" text-indent="0em"/><fo:inline id="image_arv_dcx_gt"><fo:external-graphic src="url(file:/C:/Users/sharmabi/git/documentation/helion/cinder/ceph/../../../media/ceph/screenshot-path.png)"/></fo:inline><fo:block space-after="0.6em" space-before="0.6em" text-indent="0em">You must copy the <fo:inline font-weight="bold">yml</fo:inline> files in the appropriate folder. For example: Copy
              the ring.yml file in <fo:inline font-family="monospace" font-size="10pt">config/swift/</fo:inline>.</fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item>
          <fo:list-item space-after="1.5pt" space-before="1.5pt"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()" keep-together.within-line="always" keep-with-next.within-line="always"><fo:block font-weight="bold" text-align="start"><fo:inline/>4. </fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block>Edit the configuration files, based on your environment, to deploy Ceph. </fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item>
          <fo:list-item space-after="1.5pt" space-before="1.5pt"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()" keep-together.within-line="always" keep-with-next.within-line="always"><fo:block font-weight="bold" text-align="start"><fo:inline/>5. </fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block>Edit the file <fo:inline font-family="monospace" font-size="10pt">disks_osd.yml</fo:inline> and enter the details for the additional
